headlines.description: Anthony Edwards scored 19 points and the Minnesota Timberwolves completed a perfect preseason by beating the Chicago Bulls 114-105 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Edwards scores 19 points as Timberwolves finish preseason at 5-0 by beating Bulls 114-105
